title: Opie & Jim Norton OCT 26 2015 Mon.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton OCT 26 2015 Mon (03:14:48)

On Today's Show:

MIKE TYSON, PETE DAVIDSON.

After they settle in they talk about football, someone who was killed in a cryotherapy session, and jumpers off the George Washington Bridge and Golden Gate Bridge.

Jimmy talks about going to a movie screening the other night. They listen to the "Free Beer and Hot Wings" radio show talk to Jesse Ventura about Opie and Jimmy and they talk about some of the radio people they've quarrelled with. They talk about cops.

They talk a little about Chris Rock and Bill Cosby and a few other things until Pete Davidson joins them. Then they talk about Saturday Night Live stuff until Mike Tyson joins them. They talk about fights and stuff
